    Direct Known Subclasses:
    BitArrayResource, File, HdfsFile, NullResource, OutputResource, S3FileSystemObject, ZipEntry
    public abstract class BaseWritableResource
extends BaseReadableResource
implements WritableResource
    Extends BaseReadableResource and provides a base implementation of the WritableResource interface. Adds the following methods:
    • copyFrom(Resource, CopyMode, ProgressReporter) - Copies to this resource from the given resource
    • delete() - Deletes this resource
    • println(String) - Prints the given string to this resource
    • save(InputStream, ProgressReporter) - Copies the given input to this resource

    All other methods are documented in the Resource superinterface.
